Legal Basis For Processing (EU users)
Retention period
To provide the Website to you, improve the Website and for IT security purposes.
If the processing of the Personal Data is necessary to provide the Website to you, the legal basis is contractual necessity (Article 6 (1) (b) GDPR). Further, we process the Personal Data based on our legitimate interests (Article 6 (1) (f) GDPR) to provide a secure Website to you and improve our Website.
We retain your data for the time required to ensure IT security, and, where applicable, as required or permitted by statutory law e.g. for financial statements, legal claims or archiving purposes.
